attributes.Long form description: The student disassembles a table. He first loosens the top hex socket head. Then, he unscrews the top hex socket head with the allen wrench and disassembles the top table. Lastly, the student disassembles the four legs from the table.

attributes.Transcription: All right, now we're going to disassemble this furniture, so please disassemble the shelf.

attributes.Action sentence: The student loosens the top hex socket head.
The student unscrews the top hex socket head with the Allen wrench.
The student disassembles the first leg from the table.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student drops the hex socket head.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the second leg from the table.
The student disassembles the third leg from the table.
The student disassembles the fourth leg from the table.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student accidentally drops the second hex socket head.

attributes.Transcription: Here you can press the stop button.
